Textiles, Apparel and Luxury Goods

Company Overview of Weavexx, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Weavexx, LLC manufactures and supplies paper machine clothing products. The company's products include forming and dryer fabrics and wet-end drainage equipment. It markets its products under Huytexx, Huytexx Synergie, Titan, Avantexx, Blue Maxx, and SoilMaster Black Maxx brands. The company was incorporated in 1980 and is based in Youngsville, North Carolina. Weavexx, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Xerium Technologies,Inc.


51 Flex WayYoungsville, NC 27596United StatesFounded in 1980



Phone: 919-556-7235

Fax: 919-556-2432








