Welcome to Xerium 
As a leading global developer and supplier of highly engineered products and services, Xerium continues to proudly serve a multitude of industries:

pulp, paper, paperboard and tissue
fiber and stock processing
nonwoven fabrics
building products 
other specialty industries

Our world-class technology, experienced Applications Engineering teams, and strategically located global manufacturing plants continue to deliver documented value for our customers. With our innovative patented product portfolio of fabrics, felts, belts, roll covers, SMART® Technology machine automation systems, spreader rolls, and mechanical services, Xerium continues to provide these industries with tailored solutions designed to optimize the performance of production equipment and reduce the costs of their operations.Huyck.Wangner, Weavexx, Stowe Woodward, JJ Plank, and Spencer Johnston are now united under a single global brand.


